                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You command a creature within 30 feet to Stride away from you, drop prone, or release one item it\u2019s holding. The creature can choose to perform that action as the first action on its next turn; if it doesn\u2019t, it takes 4d6 mental damage (DC 20 basic Will save).",
